transcript:
Customer: Hello?
Agent: Assalam o Alaikum, mein Ahmed bol raha hoon UBL se. Aap ki madad kese kar sakta hoon?
Customer: احمد مجھے اپنی بیلنس انکوئیری کرنی ہے
Agent: Zaroor, ab barah-e-karam apna TPIN batayen, chaar alag alag digits mein.
Agent: Shukriya. Ab apna account number verification ke liye batayen.
Customer: 12678934
Agent: Aap ke account ka balance 15,000 rupees hai. Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Customer: دوسرا اکاؤنڈ کا بھی بیلنڈ جاننے
Agent: Aap ka account balance 15,000 rupey hai. Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Customer: نہیں مجھے دوسرے اکاؤنڈ کا بیلنس بھی جاننا ہے
Agent: Agar doosre account ka balance jaana hai, to barah-e-karam uska account number bhi batayen, taake main aap ki madad kar sakoon.
Customer: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6, 7, 8
Agent: Aap ke account ka balance 50,000 rupey hai. Agar aap ka koi
Agent: Agar aap ka koi aur sawal ho to batayen.
Customer: Thank you.
Agent: Maazrat, lekin main sirf ek account ka balance bata sakta hoon. Agar aap doosre account ke liye inquiry karna chahte hain, to aapko alag se call karni hogi. UBL call karne ka shukriya. Allah Hafiz!
Agent: Maazrat, mein sirf account balance inquiry mein madad kar sakta hoon. Doosri services ke liye 111-825-888 per call karen ya apni qareeb tareen UBL branch visit karen. UBL call karne ka shukriya. Allah Hafiz!
